queries.sql: SELECT `disbursements`.*, `officers`.`username` as `officer_name`, `officers`.`campus` as `officer_campus`, `verifiers`.`username` as `verified_by_name`, `approvers`.`username` as `approved_by_name` FROM `disbursements` LEFT JOIN `users` as `officers` ON `officers`.`id` = `disbursements`.`disbursing_officer_id` LEFT JOIN `users` as `verifiers` ON `verifiers`.`id` = `disbursements`.`verified_by` LEFT JOIN `users` as `approvers` ON `approvers`.`id` = `disbursements`.`approved_by` ORDER BY `disbursements`.`created_at` DESC
